==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Numerary
<hw>Nu"mer*a*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>numerarius</ets>: cf. F. <ets>num⟦eacute⟧raire</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Belonging to a certain number; counting as one of a collection or
body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A supernumerary canon, when he obtains a prebend, becomes a
<qex>numerary</qex> canon.</q> <rj><qau>Ayliffe.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Numerate</ent>⟦br⟧
